s/0/postLink": "https://www.linkedin.com/feed/update/urn:li:activity:7343465499155959830?updateEntityUrn=urn%3Ali%3Afs_feedUpdate%3A%28V2%2Curn%3Ali%3Aactivity%3A7343465499155959830%29", "updates/0/postText": "Amari Bangsaen proudly hosted its first-ever Townhall event 🏁, themed around the thrilling world of Formula 1 racing.\nThis milestone gathering brought together team members from all departments to celebrate our progress 🎉, strengthen our culture 💪, and align on the exciting journey ahead 🚀.\n\nOne of the highlights of the event was a thought-provoking session on identifying our “Strong Why” 💡—an exercise designed to help each team member connect with their personal and collective purpose within the organization. This was followed by an engaging “Boat Rolling” activity 🚣‍♂️, emphasizing the importance of unity, clear communication 🗣️, and synchronized teamwork 🤝. It was an energizing reminder that we move faster and further when we row in the same direction.\n\nAs part of our transformation journey under “Amari: The Shining Way” ✨, the Townhall also featured a Uniform Fashion Show 👕, where team members proudly showcased our new uniforms. This reflects our refreshed identity, elevated professionalism, and renewed focus on delivering heartfelt service ❤️ with a modern touch.\n\nThe day culminated in a meaningful Pin of Pride Ceremony 🏅, honoring team members for their commitment, passion, and embodiment of Amari values 🌟. This recognition reinforces our belief that our people are our greatest strength 💖.\n\nThe event not only celebrated our achievements but also set the tone for an exciting new chapter at Amari Bangsaen—fueled by purpose, driven by teamwork, and dressed for success. 🏨✨\n\n🙏 A special thank you to Saranya Watanasirisuk, PCC, Harold Olaya Leon and Sukamal Mondal - SEPC, CIS from ONYX Corporate Office for their inspiring speeches and presence. Your words energized the team and reinforced the vision we are all working toward together.\n\nONYX Hospitality Group, Amari Bangsaen People & Passion\n\n\n#AmariBangsaen #Townhall2025 #TheShiningWay #PurposeDriven #HeartfeltService #TeamAlignment #PinOfPride #StrongerTogether #HospitalityExcellence #F1InspiredLeadership #UniformReveal #CultureInAction #ONYXSupport #Turnmomentsintomemories #Onyx #Onyxhospitality #ATB", "updates/0/type": "Post", "urn": "ACoAABGZzgEBXWe3AO5aut-OJqsX5FQ_AT6i6CA"}$$::jsonb),
