lbert is the definition of high performance, high output. He charges into every task with his full attention and energy and because of this consistently achieves above average results in remarkable time frames. He is creatives, dependable, hardworking, and consistent. Working with Albert is a pleasure. ", "recommendationsReceived/8/name": "Edmund Lowman", "recommendationsReceived/8/subtitle": "Entrepreneur and Investor", "recommendationsReceived/8/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/edmund-lowman-984923156/", "recommendationsReceived/8/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAACWDB7QBoPQ8OFkwWIOjLAp5hhbv8tj-bzg", "recommendationsReceived/9/context": "Le Thuy Tuong worked with Albert on the same team", "recommendationsReceived/9/date": "June 19, 2018", "recommendationsReceived/9/description": "As Albert’s HR Manager during his time at ‘The Deck Group’, I've benefited from his creative problem-solving, tireless work ethic, and willingness to do whatever it takes to create a product that will translate the customer's vision into reality. \nAs a colleague, Albert is incredibly generous with his time and expertise, which includes everything from over 15 years of hospitality management experience to an expert-level knowledge of Food and Beverage. Beyond that, his co-worker, I have to say that his humor and good nature make long nights and tough deadlines much easier on his team. \nI give Albert my warmest recommendations and wish him all the best in the future.", "recommendationsReceived/9/name": "Le Thuy Tuong Vy", "recommendationsReceived/9/subtitle": "Human resource Manager", "recommendationsReceived/9/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/le-thuy-tuong-vy-03042950/", "recommendationsReceived/9/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAq9zuQBMth1bEQpvhLAop64yU3AFLNDAzk", "recommendationsReceived/10/context": "Adrienne worked with Albert on the same team", "recommendationsReceived/10/date": "June 11, 2018", "recommendationsReceived/10/description": "I had the opportunity to work with and learn from Albert during my time working as a consultant for The Factory Art Centre (FCAC) in Ho Chi Minh City, in 2016 to 2017. I was part of recruiting Albert to the position of General manager in which I saw him structure and develop the concept and team to make them ready for launching this, for Vietnam, ground-breaking initiative.\n\nIn my experience Albert is a hard working, quality driven, passionate, creative and very loyal colleague, with the biggest heart. He loves for his team and always enters a project with the highest level of commitment. Albert challenged my in my leadership capacities and business sense, and I appreciate the insight and personal growth that I gained.\n\nAlbert’s creativity, delicate eye for details and concepts is invaluable, and I am sure he can bring life to any project he would be entrusted.\n\n I give Albert my warmest recommendations and wish him the best of luck in his future endeavours!", "recommendationsReceived/10/name": "Adrienne De Geer", "recommendationsReceived/10/subtitle": "Coach, Connector and Creative Social Entrepreneur with 20+ years of living in Eastern Europe and Asia, actively inviting Change as a catalyst to grow stronger wings.", "recommendationsReceived/10/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/adrienne-de-geer-111594b/", "recommendationsReceived/10/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAILIJ0BOutSiddpJK6sNMJTGDCni97ZLSU", "recommendationsReceived/11/context": "Edina reported directly to Albert", "recommendationsReceived/11/date": "November 8, 2016", "recommendationsReceived/11/description": "I had a pleasure to work with Albert in London and in South East Asia too. Albert is truly an inspiring leader, someone who communicates clearly, concisely, and often, and by doing so motivates everyone to give his or her best all the time. He is decisive by nature - putting things into perspective, to weigh up the options, to assess all relevant information and crucially to anticipate the consequences, good and bad. Being mentored by Albert given me the opportunity to grow in the industry and to believe nothing is impossible!!! ", "recommendationsReceived/11/name": "Edina Sipocz", "recommendationsReceived/11/subtitle": "Lifestyle Manager", "recommendationsReceived/11/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/edina-sipocz/", "recommendationsReceived/11/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAB1n0XABZOkwhgv4_Z4hSU0n6vvJpylssUU", "recommendationsReceived/12/context": "Sandra worked with Albert on the same team", "recommendationsReceived/12/date": "January 2, 2015", "recommendationsReceived/12/description": "Very professional and knowledgeable, striving for high customer service at all times.\nIt was a great pleasure working with Albert during his successful F&B  project with The Arch London hotel.\n", "recommendationsReceived/12/name": "Sandra Nunes MIH", "recommendationsReceived/12/subtitle": "People and Development Director in an amazing location of Portugal called Comporta and part of Discovery Land Company", "recommendationsReceived/12/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/sandra-nunes-london/", "recommendationsReceived/12/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAARS9UMBr-waWEnoQcAbiNUH8TACFGscM6Q", "recommendationsReceived/13/context": "Gemma worked with Albert on the same team", "recommendationsReceived/13/date": "October 22, 2014", "recommendationsReceived/13/description": "I had the pleasure of working with Albert for a year at the Aviator hotel, collaborating on several hotel projects. Albert is a very driven, passionate and personable individual. He has an incredible eye for detail and is incredibly focused on creating the best experience for the hotels clients. No matter how tense a meeting, Albert made sure everyone left work with a smile. ", "recommendationsReceived/13/name": "Gemma P.", "recommendationsReceived/13/subtitle": "Head of Commercialisation and Finance Support", "recommendationsReceived/13/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/gemma-p-35249182/", "recommendationsReceived/13/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAABG